commit message: #13 Using CalendarContract fields for start and end date in intent.
Refactored calendar event integration to use a provider mechanism.
#17 Events that span multiple days now create multiple entries.
#15 Touching a calendar entry now provides visual touch feedback.

#17 Fixed a problem where opening an event in the calendar would show
incorrect dates when the event was spanning multiple days.
#19 Events without a title now indicate that there is no title.
#18 Spanning events now only show up starting from today.
Updated versionName to '1.3' and versionCode to '5'.
Updated English date format description string.
